<L>__{exterior bwi airport day}
<A>__{jane's cab pulls up to the curb. she gets out she is carrying no luggage. she sees tom who hurriedly walks up to her. jane is fighting to maintain a calm.}
<C>__{tom}
<D>__{look who's the organized one. i've got everything.}
<A>__{he briefly opens a paper gift shop bag he is holding and shows her he has bought them each a bathing suit.}
