<D>__{i'm not going.}
<A>__{he looks at her with anticipatory distaste evident on his face.}
<C>__{tom}
<D>__{why?}
<C>__{jane}
<D>__{i saw the taped outtakes of the interview with the girl. i know you 'acted' your reaction after the interview.}
